sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SF as Salesforce
    participant IN as Webhook Ingress
    participant EB as Event Bus
    participant T as Temporal (CloseDealSaga)
    participant ID as Idempotency DB
    participant QB as QuickBooks
    participant SL as Slack

    SF->>IN: Opportunity Closed (webhook)
    IN->>IN: Validate signature
    IN->>EB: Publish deal.closed
    EB->>T: Start workflow (dealId: D-123)

    T->>ID: Check qb:invoice:D-123
    alt Already completed
        ID-->>T: Cached invoiceId
    else Not exists
        T->>QB: Create Invoice (idempotency-key: D-123)
        QB-->>T: invoiceId INV-456
        T->>ID: Store completed + response
    end

    T->>ID: Check slack:deal-won:D-123
    alt Slack already sent
        ID-->>T: Skip
    else Send notification
        T->>SL: Post #sales-wins
        alt Slack fails (429/5xx)
            SL-->>T: Error
            T->>T: Retry with backoff (max 5x)
            Note over T: Invoice NOT rolled back
        else Success
            SL-->>T: OK
            T->>ID: Store completed
        end
    end

    T->>EB: Publish deal.workflow.completed
